OL,3,CAlleged Irish crime boss Daniel
OL,4,CKinahan arrested in Dubai
OL,6,FDaniel Kinahan, alleged to be a leader
OL,7,Fof the Kinahan organised crime group,
OL,8,Fhas been arrested in the United Arab
OL,9,FEmirates.
OL,11,FIrish police said they were aware of
OL,12,Fthe arrest of a man in his late 40s.
OL,13,FDubai Police said the arrest took
OL,14,Fplace on April 15.
OL,16,FThe High Court in Dublin previously
OL,17,Fnamed Kinahan, who lives in the UAE,
OL,18,Fas a senior figure in an organised
OL,19,Fcrime gang involved in international
OL,20,Fdrug trafficking operations and
OL,21,Ffirearm offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
