OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776506752
OL,3,CAlleged Irish crime boss Daniel
OL,4,CKinahan arrested in Dubai
OL,6,FThe Kinahan cartel was involved in a
OL,7,Ffeud with the rival Hutch crime gang
OL,8,Fin Ireland, which began in 2015, and
OL,9,Fwent on to claim the lives of 18
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FIn 2016, an attempt was made on Daniel
OL,13,FKinahan's life at a boxing weigh-in at
OL,14,Fthe Regency Hotel in Dublin.
OL,16,FDubai Police said they had arrested an
OL,17,F"Irish fugitive for his alleged role
OL,18,Fin an international organised crime
OL,19,Fnetwork".
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@HO]
