OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776506752
OL,3,CAlleged Irish crime boss Daniel
OL,4,CKinahan arrested in Dubai
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The arrest
OL,7,Ffollowed the receipt of a judicial
OL,8,Ffile from Irish authorities detailing
OL,9,Fthe suspect's alleged crimes and his
OL,10,Finvolvement in an international
OL,11,Fcriminal organisation.
OL,13,F"Based on the file, Dubai public
OL,14,Fprosecution issued an arrest warrant
OL,15,Fto initiate legal procedures ahead of
OL,16,Fhis extradition.
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
