OL,3,CAlleged Irish crime boss Daniel
OL,4,CKinahan arrested in Dubai
OL,6,F"Specialised teams immediately
OL,7,Flaunched intensive search and
OL,8,Fsurveillance operations, leading to
OL,9,Fthe suspect's capture within 48 hours
OL,10,Fof the warrant being issued."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FKinahan's involvement in boxing caused
OL,18,Fcontroversy in 2020 when heavyweight
OL,19,FTyson Fury thanked him for reaching an
OL,20,Fagreement for him to take on Anthony
OL,21,FJoshua.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
