OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776506752
OL,3,CAlleged Irish crime boss Daniel
OL,4,CKinahan arrested in Dubai
OL,6,FFury said he was responsible for
OL,7,Forganising "the biggest fight in
OL,8,FBritish boxing history".
OL,10,FBut within weeks, Fury's team
OL,11,Fannounced that Kinahan would no longer
OL,12,Fnegotiate for him.
OL,14,FIn 2022, US authorities issued a
OL,15,Freward of up to 5 million dollars for
OL,16,Fhis arrest.
