OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776506752
OL,3,CAlleged Irish crime boss Daniel
OL,4,CKinahan arrested in Dubai
OL,6,FThe US Treasury department imposed
OL,7,Fsanctions against senior members of
OL,8,Fthe Kinahan crime gang, including
OL,9,FChristy Kinahan Snr and his sons
OL,10,FDaniel and Christopher Jnr.
OL,12,FWhile Kinahan left Ireland years ago,
OL,13,Fthe investigation by gardai continued.
OL,14,FThey recently secured a warrant for
OL,15,Fhis arrest in the High Court in Dublin.
OL,17,FA gardai statement said the arrest was
OL,18,Fan "important demonstration of the
OL,19,Fneed for international law enforcement
OL,20,Fco-operation in tackling transnational
OL,21,Forganised crime".
